Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, if you're
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,into AI and automation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, that speed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and efficiency are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter programmatic tool, calling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,this feature, let's cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,execute code directly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with external tools, slashing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,latency, like a hot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,knife through butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine running
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a multi tool workflow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,without the annoying round
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,trips to the model.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So how does this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,magic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, programmatic tool, calling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,minimizes token consumption by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,filtering data
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,before it even hits
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the model's context window.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Less data means faster
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold on to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,make this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to enable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the code execution tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bring
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this to life with
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a real world example.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine querying sales data
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,across multiple regions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with programmatic tool, calling,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,cloud, can aggregate the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,results in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You would use a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,curl command to make
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the API call specifying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,headers and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,data structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This example uses the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,model cloud opus 4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,6 with a token
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,limit of 4 ,096.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's dive deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,into how the API
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,works.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:00:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The tools array in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,your API request specifies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the type and name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of the tool for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,code execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This allows for a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,seamless integration with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,various external tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind though,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that the data retention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,policy is standard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and not covered by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,zero data retention ZDR.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So why should you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,care about programmatic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,tool, calling because it's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a game changer for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,any developer or business
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that needs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to optimize workflows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The reduction in latency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and token usage means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you can get more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,done in less time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So get out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,enable that code execution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,tool and start harnessing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of programmatic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,tool, calling today.
